{"tid":1672312,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"［未食藥］葉劉倡名店大減價助治療市民創傷","createTime":"2019-10-24T04:37:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-24T05:35:55.000Z","uid":247122,"like":3,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"7bc9a46c6800761c34ad2b7b1a0c598d1959566f","tid":1672312,"uid":247122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T04:37:41.000Z","msg":"立法會正審議稅務條例修訂草案，多名議員表示支持，但認為政府近月推出對各界的支援措施不足。  <br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">新民黨香港島議員葉劉淑儀稱：「所謂的針對性，其實是『擠牙膏』的方法，是好還是不好呢，司長？對提振經濟的作用有多少呢？局長你有否想過呼籲香港的名店一起宣布何時為了治療市民的創傷，全部名店、大商場大減價？」  </span></strong><br />\n<br />\n立法會審議《2019年稅務(修例)(稅務寬免)條例草案》原訂在六月處理，但其後因為大樓受破壞推延至今。  <br />\n<br />\n政府早前提出修正案，將2018年至2019年度的薪俸稅、個人入息課稅及利得稅退稅率由《預算案》的百分之七十五，提升至百分百，上限維持兩萬元。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.tvb.com/local/5db11086e6038301683557d0/立法會審議稅務條例修訂草案-多名議員表示支持\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvb.com%2Flocal%2F5db11086e6038301683557d0%2F%E7%AB%8B%E6%B3%95%E6%9C%83%E5%AF%A9%E8%AD%B0%E7%A8%85%E5%8B%99%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B%E4%BF%AE%E8%A8%82%E8%8D%89%E6%A1%88-%E5%A4%9A%E5%90%8D%E8%AD%B0%E5%93%A1%E8%A1%A8%E7%A4%BA%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81&d=pzn6Hq8jxzH2PmSSbZvUoTbTr8NPmLdj%2FTsGYWOA6so%3D&h=37ef556c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.tvb.com/local/5db11086e6038301683557d0/立法會審議稅務條例修訂草案-多名議員表示支持</a>"},{"pid":"aaef57bc2adfffc7e2f09d7bf0efcef01abae982","tid":1672312,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T04:38:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>【SUCK／1026】長龍爆買日 - 黃店存貨壓力測試（2）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1672101\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1672101</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gv2xOLu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fgv2xOLu.jpg&h=a9eb1a8f&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"ffe0b50128a267e46426a3a84b1651cbaf2d39e3","tid":1672312,"uid":212626,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T04:41:21.000Z","msg":"又想益收成期<img src=\"/assets/fa